{
  "texts": [
    "This step employs a visual tokenizer (e.g., Q-Former [23], linear projection [29] or the Resampler [1]) to map the visual features encoded by a pre-trained vision backbone (e.g.",
    "EVA-CLIP [10]) to visual tokens within the feature space of the foundation LLM.",
    "In this way, the projected visual tokens of an image carry its visual features.",
    "• Integrated Analysis.",
    "After obtaining the projected visual tokens of each image, the model fuses them with the textual tokens of the instruction using cross-modal attention mechanisms [45]."
  ]
}